{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In 1988, a body of a Frogman has been found dead.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Presumed cause of death: Drowning</h2><br>In 1988, a dead body was found at a riverside and sent to the morgue for autopsy.<br>During the autopsy, a lot of irregularities were found on his body.<br>As you collect evidence at the scene of the crime and find more information...<br>Who is the real culprit? Why was the victim killed? What was the motive for the murder?<br><br><br>Are you ready to uncover the truth?<br><br>\u201cFor Your Tranquility\u201d is an investigation game where you become a Medical Examiner and uncover the truth by collecting evidence, performing autopsies, and investigating crime scenes to solve the case. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183320/extras/CrimeScene.png?t=1674216050\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collect evidence from the crime scene.</h2>The smallest clue can be the key to solving the case! Even the seemingly trivial might be a key piece of evidence.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183320/extras/autopsy.png?t=1674216050\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Use various pieces of equipment in the autopsy room to collect evidence.</h2>Magnifying glass, cotton swab, tweezers, scalpel to analyze the body and find out the truth.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183320/extras/ScreenShot7.png?t=1674216050\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Case Log</h2>The evidence you find will be logged to the case log. Check the log and solve the crime!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endings based on your deductions</h2>You have collected a lot of evidence and made your deduction. It is now time to check if you have solved the case. <br>If your deductions are correct, the truth will be revealed. Otherwise, the case will go unsolved, forever.","achievements":{"hig